{"tid":2377100,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"亞洲人係咪好嫌棄自己?","createTime":"2021-01-23T10:16:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-23T10:21:59.000Z","uid":324681,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"621619fc8b94d0cc9dd3a7494c8b86825b2784d7","tid":2377100,"uid":324681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T10:16:53.000Z","msg":"好多亞洲人都係鍾意歐美面孔。<br />\n化妝整容都要整到自己成個鬼婆咁。<br />\n但未見過有鬼婆會想自己整到成個亞洲人咁。<br />\n天生黑頭就要染啡佢。<br />\n褐色眼珠要戴啡色con.<br />\n將自己扁鼻整到高一高。<br />\n成日嫌眼細，覺得大眼先靚。"},{"pid":"930376ae22fabbe9b9be53b49fdc1460879869d3","tid":2377100,"uid":54930,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T10:19:46.000Z","msg":"因為眼大鼻高真係靚<br />\n就算套落邊個人種都好<br />\n不過髮色同眼珠其實見人見智<br />\n我自己覺得黑髮最靚"},{"pid":"e613f2b2a78bae8a3f60d18d10ba80f4cc15e7df","tid":2377100,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T10:19:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%A4%96%E5%9C%8B%E7%89%88%E8%9B%87%E7%B2%BE%E7%94%B7-%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E8%B6%85%E7%B4%9A%E7%B2%89%E7%B5%B2%E8%B1%AA%E7%A0%B876%E8%90%AC%E6%B8%AF%E5%B9%A3%E6%95%B4%E5%AE%B9%E8%AE%8A%E9%9F%93%E6%98%9F-061832165.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%25A4%2596%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%2589%2588%25E8%259B%2587%25E7%25B2%25BE%25E7%2594%25B7-%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%259C%258B%25E8%25B6%2585%25E7%25B4%259A%25E7%25B2%2589%25E7%25B5%25B2%25E8%25B1%25AA%25E7%25A0%25B876%25E8%2590%25AC%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25B9%25A3%25E6%2595%25B4%25E5%25AE%25B9%25E8%25AE%258A%25E9%259F%2593%25E6%2598%259F-061832165.html&d=m1YmCj491ZwsIKcmlD2TahnxOJLX742lx1SCoot1iYY%3D&h=8d29cda8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%A4%96%E5%9C%8B%E7%89%88%E8%9B%87%E7%B2%BE%E7%94%B7-%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E8%B6%85%E7%B4%9A%E7%B2%89%E7%B5%B2%E8%B1%AA%E7%A0%B876%E8%90%AC%E6%B8%AF%E5%B9%A3%E6%95%B4%E5%AE%B9%E8%AE%8A%E9%9F%93%E6%98%9F-061832165.html</a>"},{"pid":"d6a31c882f3e6cfe6982d27d6d16f48abbffd929","tid":2377100,"uid